Speaker 2: Yeah, I'm calling to cancel my subscription today.

Speaker 2: 55130.

Speaker 1: Sean?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Perfect, perfect. Looks like you just got that second order on your VIP prescription.

Speaker 1: No problem. I'll take care of that for you.

Speaker 2: Now, Mr. Peeper, once I do cancel, I won't be able to open this prescription back up for you in the future, though.

Speaker 1: Okay, so you will have to go somewhere else to get the pills.

Speaker 2: It could be a cheap vendor, get them from India, China.

Speaker 1: It would be really, really bad for you.

Speaker 2: So with this being said, are you sure you want me to finalize that for you?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir, please. Thank you.

Speaker 2: No problem, no problem.

Speaker 1: All righty, Mr. Peeper, I went ahead and took care of that for you, so you're all set.

Speaker 2: The account has been all canceled out. You're good to go. Thank you.

Speaker 1: Awesome. I appreciate your help today. Have a wonderful afternoon.

Speaker 2: You too. Bye now.
